Description: Following you recent article below it has been advised that we upgrade to EPP v5.9.4.1

Please advise how we can achieve this as a cloud hosted client?

Thank You in advance
Steps to Reproduce Updated: To upgrade the server version from Live Update.

What We've Learned Updated: The scheduled Update did not go through.
I have asked him to cancel the scheduled one, and to perform it manually.
Next Steps Updated: Check for updates, and apply them
